## Test Organization & Naming
- **Location**: Organize tests in `test/contract/`, `test/unit/`, `test/e2e/`, `test/integration/`
- **Naming**: `t_<component>_<test_type>.py` (e.g., `t_loader_formats.py`)
- **Functions**: `test_<scenario>_<expected>()` (e.g., `test_load_pdf_extracts_text()`)
- **Classes**: `Test<Component>` per module

## Deprecation Review Checklist
- [ ] Are current contract tests still valid for refactored code?
- [ ] Are unit tests testing current component interfaces?
